cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CL 

This paper deals with automatic image annotation, which is a problem in computer vision and pattern recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with semantic embedding and label transfer, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions social media and user-generated tags, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
